properties.Name: Coupon
properties.Description: A ticket or document or physical collateral that may be exchanged for a product either in full, discounted amount or discounted percentage. Sometimes referred to as a voucher.

Columns.Name: CouponId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a coupon.

Columns.Name: CouponStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the coupon is effective.

Columns.Name: CouponEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the coupon is effective.

Columns.Name: CouponDiscountPercent
Columns.Description: The percent discount that is offered when the coupon is utilized.

Columns.Name: CouponMaximumDiscountValue
Columns.Description: The maximum discount value that can be achieved by using the coupon.

Columns.Name: CouponFaceValue
Columns.Description: The face value of the coupon.

Columns.Name: GlobalCouponNumber
Columns.Description: The Global Coupon Number (GCN) is used to identify coupon offers and if needed the individually issued coupons via the optional serial component. The GCN is part of the GS1 system of standards.

Columns.Name: CouponNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the coupon.
